data.description: Pending-Release. Welcome to this charming two bedroom townhome tucked away in Congress Heights! An enclosed front porch greets you as you arrive and is perfect for enjoying a morning cup of coffee or lounging. Showcasing a neutral color palette, light-filled windows, hardwood flooring on the main level, and ceiling fans throughout. Kick your feet up in the front living room and crown molding that continues into the spacious dining room that is also adorned with accent chair railing. Prepare your favorite meals in the kitchen with stainless steel appliances including a refrigerator and gas range. The primary bedroom suite highlights a soaring cathedral ceiling and a second bedroom and full bathroom complete the upper level. Watch your favorite television shows and movies in the expansive recreation room in the lower level. The fenced front and rear yards provide plenty of space for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. Fantastic location close to I-295, Congress Heights Metro Station, Joint Base Anacostia-Bolling, Entertainment & Sports Arena and more!
